    <item>
      <title>印度从俄罗斯转向美国寻求尖端武器</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/india-pivots-from-russia-to-us-for-cutting-edge-weapons</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度官员称，印度已大幅减少对俄罗斯的国防装备订单，目前正从西方供应商处购买更多武器，对于一个传统上依赖莫斯科武器的国家来说，这是一个重大的政策转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/india-pivots-from-russia-to-us-for-cutting-edge-weapons</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 07:11:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>因担心关税，许多中国铜贸易商暂停进口美国废铜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/many-china-copper-traders-halt-us-scrap-imports-on-tariff-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[北京安泰科信息发展有限公司称，由于预计唐纳德·特朗普就任总统后将征收关税，许多中国金属进口商已停止购买美国废铜。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/many-china-copper-traders-halt-us-scrap-imports-on-tariff-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 04:03:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员无视中国对人民币的支持，导致人民币跌至一年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/china-s-yuan-falls-to-one-year-low-on-tariff-risk-dollar-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员们无视中国支撑人民币的努力，导致人民币跌至一年来的最低点，因为他们押注决策者将不得不继续放松货币政策来重振经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-03/china-s-yuan-falls-to-one-year-low-on-tariff-risk-dollar-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Dec 2024 01:35:59 GMT</pubDate>
